tspan.tspan: 1. Play Diplomacy Game – Thumbs Up or
Finger Gun w/Player next in Initiative
Order.
a. Both Thumbs Up – You get 2 DI, they
get 1 DI.
b. Finger Gun and Thumbs Up – Finger
Gun gets 3 DI, Thumbs Up gets 0 DI.
c. Both Finger Gun – Both get 0 DI.
2. Diplomatic Actions – In Initiative Order,
may do any of the following actions:
a. Place Diplomatic Influence on
Principalities. To ally, you need 1 DI
province, and more than all other
Players.
b. Trade Gold for DI at a rate of 1:1.
c. Replace a town-province of yours
with a new Prince. You’re its ally with 2
DI.
d. Gift adjacent, same-religion, non-
town province to Principality for 1 DI
with it.
